      <title>高盛警告看跌风险，欧洲天然气价格下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/european-gas-prices-slip-as-goldman-warns-of-bearish-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团警告称，近期飙升至今年高点的价格存在下行风险，导致欧洲天然气价格下跌。]]></description>
